headline: Agoda and Archipelago International Partner to Capture Indonesia's Growing Travel Demand
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has announced a new partnership with Archipelago International, Southeast Asia's largest privately owned hotel management company, to broaden traveler choice and strengthen both brands' regional presence.

content.title: Agoda and Archipelago International Partner to Capture Indonesia's Growing Travel Demand
content.summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has announced a new partnership with Archipelago International, Southeast Asia's largest privately owned hotel management company, to broaden traveler choice and strengthen both brands' regional presence.
